com.interpss.core.dclf
Interface ILossFactor

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
DclfAlgorithm
All Known Implementing Classes:
DclfAlgorithmImpl
public interface ILossFactor
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'ILoss Factor'. calculate network loss factor with one inject bus and one or many withdraw bus(es) by injecting a 1.0pu current into the injection bus and withdraw the current from the the withdraw bus(es).

See Also:
DclfPackage.getILossFactor()
